[NPC] Trasok: Hmmm...
[NPC] Trasok: an interesting commission.
[NPC] Trasok: None of my business, though.
[NPC] Trasok: I'll need a gold ingot to start work on it.
[NPC] Trasok: Bring one to me, and I'll be heating up the forge in the meantime.

